name: Dating Naked
overview: A reality series in which a man and a woman date two different naked suitors on a remote exotic location.

episodes.name: Joe & Wee Wee
episodes.overview: On the premiere episode of Dating Naked, two daring singles, Joe and Wee Wee, each go on three romantic, adventurous, tropical dates in the hopes of making a lasting connection. But if they want to find love, they'll have to bare it all! Joe and Wee Wee will try their hand at body painting, boogie-boarding, sea tubing, bird-watching and even zorbing in a giant hamster ball. Relationships will be forged and feelings may get hurt...and they'll do it all completely naked.

episodes.name: Steven and Taryn
episodes.overview: Steven, the self-proclaimed "King of the Nerds", and Taryn, a sexy San Francisco blonde, have come to paradise in search of a naked love connection.

episodes.name: Keegan and Diane
episodes.overview: Diane is a vivacious blonde looking for the man of her dreams while Keegan is a buff rogue on the prowl for just the right girl.

episodes.name: Chuck and Camille
episodes.overview: Chuck, a fast talking swimwear designer from Miami and Camille, an edgy Las Vegas bartender have come to paradise looking for love. But only by putting it all out there will they be able to experience dating in it's purist form - totally nude. During their quest they will each go on three dates and experience yachting, cigar rolling, wine tasting and even a little bit of yoga, all while in their birthday suits.

episodes.name: Mike and Candace
episodes.overview: Mike, an accountant from Long Island, first meets gorgeous Los Angeles native Candace. These two singles bravely bare it all on three naked dates in search of a real connection. Presented by VH1.

episodes.name: Greg and Ashley
episodes.overview: Greg, a formerly shy accountant turned MMA fighter, and Ashley a free-spirited artist from Denver, Colorado come to a romantic private island with the hope that finding a match might still be possible. But if they want to get their date on, they'll have to take their clothes off.

episodes.name: AJ and Liddy
episodes.overview: Having had no luck on the dating scene back home, AJ and Liddy arrive in paradise eager for a shot at true love. Wearing only a smile and some sunblock, the two will go on three dates and enjoy such activities as a banana boat ride, a buried treasure hunt, riding trail horses and even a good old fashioned game of beer pong!

episodes.name: Mike and Moenay
episodes.overview: Accomplished player Mike(y) has no trouble cheekily flaunting his fine physique frock-less and charming three dates in a row, starting with Moenay, who expects too much. Next comes Stephanie, an airhead party girl but to his taste. Neither girl has any interest in studly 'old' Dan, who is preoccupied with weird vibes 'lifestyle' theory. The third man bails out without even seeing Moenay, who tries to catch up with Stephanie, who already spent the night with Mikey, by kissing, but isn't chosen.

episodes.name: Sean and Juliet
episodes.overview: Sean is an ex-Marine from Philadelphia on a recon mission for romance. Juliet is a British dance instructor looking for a permanent Tango partner. The hunt for love has brought the two of them to a tropical paradise where they will strip down for dates with three eager - and likewise unclothed - partners. Sean and Juliet will participate in an inflatable human hamster ball race, bocce ball match, trampoline acrobatics, and jungle ATV-ing -- all while stark naked.

episodes.name: The Wedding
episodes.overview: Having found a rare and soulful connection on the island, Ashley and Alika have decided to face the naked truth...they're in love and they want to get married.

episodes.name: Joe & MJ
episodes.overview: Two adventurous singles - Joe, a business owner from Newport Beach, California, and MJ, a product specialist from Detroit, Michigan - take their quest to find a perfect match to a private tropical locale. Three romantic and thrilling dates await each of them featuring activities such as snorkeling, golfing, jet-skiing, yoga and sailing. The catch? They're going to do it all in the buff. Only when MJ and Joe are fully exposed can love be truly blind.

episodes.name: Strip Down & Buckle Up
episodes.overview: The Season 2 premiere of the "au naturel" dating series features two singles arriving on an island in the Philippines where they'll spend 10 weeks. Each week, two new men and two new women will join them, with the primary daters picking one to stay.

episodes.name: Catch & Release
episodes.overview: Chris must choose between a Texas girly-girl and a good ol' gal from North Carolina; and Kerri tries to connect with a nervous New Yorker and a dreamy surfer.

episodes.name: Frontrunners & Back Burners
episodes.overview: Kerri fears that Chris is losing interest; Chris goes water couching with Mariah and plasters the backside of model Fallon; and Kerri gives a nude massage to Frankie and is serenaded by Mason.

episodes.name: Check & Mate
episodes.overview: Chris and Kerri agree to put their feelings for each other aside as they have each found a perfect Keeper. But those bonds will be tested as four new daters arrive on the island to compete for attention with an impromptu strip-off!

episodes.name: Two Young & Too Restless
episodes.overview: With two serious Keepers in the house, the new daters have their work cut out for them. Curvy Stephanie and feisty Andrea vie for Chris's affections. Meanwhile, pro-wrestler Mark and suave Italian Domenico hope to win Kerri's heart.

episodes.name: Big Fights & Bald Heads
episodes.overview: Kerri struggles to watch Chris' relationship with his Keeper continue to grow. Chris plays a sweaty, naked game of basketball with Lauryn and gets dance lessons from bald, bodybuilder Amanda. Kerri's luck may change when Justin, a gorgeous personal trainer and stand up comic Doug arrive.

episodes.name: Smooches & Sabotages
episodes.overview: After a volleyball match with a Dating Naked veteran and a game of dress up with the vivacious Carrie, Chris must decide to move on or dig deeper with his Keeper. Kerri and her Keeper are hot and heavy but she's got two new dates on the horizon. Perhaps a new cowboy will lasso her heart or maybe a tattooed band manager will strike the right chord.

episodes.name: Passive & Aggressive
episodes.overview: The sparks aren't exactly flying for Chris, Kerri and their respective Keepers. Bad boy Dan and budding mogul Wilson step in to try to light Kerri's flame. Jokey, tomboy Erica and beautiful, bar top girl, Elissa attempt to steal Chris's heart.

episodes.name: Eavesdroppers & Ultimatums
episodes.overview: With their time on the island nearing an end, Kerri reveals her true feelings for Chris and wants to know how he feels. But with both of them already having potential matches in the house and more dates on the way, it may be too little too late.

episodes.name: Arrivals & Departures
episodes.overview: It's the season finale and the tension is at its peak! Chris and Kerri must choose who has captured their hearts. Will it be one of their daters or could it be each other? Their decisions shock everyone as their final choices are revealed.

episodes.name: Stripped & Searching
episodes.overview: Two singles, Natalie and David, arrive in beautiful Bora Bora where they'll spend the next twelve weeks looking for love free from distraction and clothes. When Natalie's first date, Vinny, goes off the rails, dashing lifeguard Zakk comes to her rescue. Sexy nurse Dorothy gets David's pulse racing but she gets some competition from female bodybuilder, Nadica.

episodes.name: Two-Faces & Suitcases
episodes.overview: David realizes that he may regret keeping high-maintenance Nadica. Luckily, he has party girl Vanessa and sexy, competitive Nicole vying for his attention. Natalie's Keeper, Zakk, is falling hard but his honesty comes into question after a run-in with one of the other daters.

episodes.name: Drag & Drop
episodes.overview: When David brings free-spirit Georgie and bombshell redhead Sarah back to the house, his Keeper, Nicole, gets possessive. Zakk's insecurity becomes an issue when he meets Natalie's new daters, successful businessman Sam and spacey, fun loving, Darius.

episodes.name: Vamps & Gramps
episodes.overview: Natalie dates golf-pro Tweed and Bob, who is old enough to be her grandfather. David's date with Ona is an emotional rollercoaster, and his second date, Kendra, turns from nice to naughty when she feels threatened by Natalie and David's flirtation.

episodes.name: Shark Bait & Heartbreak
episodes.overview: Natalie finds herself playing third wheel to David and Sarah's blossoming romance. But her fortunes reverse after she jumps into shark infested waters with culturally-confused David and hits the outdoor gym with muscular JT.

episodes.name: Lap Dances & Second Chances
episodes.overview: Natalie's new dates, a sexy male exotic dancer named "Magic J." and a tall ginger named Drew try to steal her away from her Keeper. David grows jealous of Natalie's connections, until he meets beautiful Jaclyn, and feisty Varshay.

episodes.name: Pub Crawls & Great Balls
episodes.overview: David's card is full with his tribal dance partner Daizha and his Italian cooking classmate, Alexa. Natalie bounces from self-described former "Guido" Lance and anatomically gifted D'Andre.

episodes.name: Reset & Game On
episodes.overview: Friction between Natalie and David comes to a head. David exposes himself like never before as he performs aerial yoga with Noelle while Natalie ends up in a sticky situation with Tommy.

episodes.name: Hit It & Quit It
episodes.overview: Natalie's strong connection with her Keeper is challenged when stuntman Connor flips his way into her heart. When David's date, hot model Michelle, arrives on the scene, the undeniable chemistry puts everyone on notice.

episodes.name: Kiss & Don't Tell
episodes.overview: Natalie and David's relationship takes a major leap, so the Keepers must step up their game. It's a tug-of-war for Natalie's affections while David is just trying to stay afloat with his new dates.

episodes.name: Chakras & Awe
episodes.overview: With two serious Keepers in the mix and more new dates on the way, an unexpected turn means David and Natalie must confront what their relationship means to them, and to the people vying for their hearts.

episodes.name: Returns & Exchanges
episodes.overview: After 12 weeks, things get even more complicated as a new pair of old flames return to the island to heat things up. The time has come: David and Natalie must choose their final Keeper.
